  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Efficient Management",
      "text": "Introducing the MikroTik CRS354-48P-4S+2Q+RM, a rackmount switch designed to efficiently manage networks in demanding environments. With its exceptional functionality and the most competitive price point available, it's an ideal addition to any professional setup. This advanced solution offers unmatched performance, making it the top pick for system administrators."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Flexibility & Scalability",
      "text": "The CRS354-48P-4S+2Q+RM features 48 x 1G RJ45 ports, 4 x 10G SFP+ ports, and 2 x 40G QSFP+ ports, establishing an advanced level of connectivity that ensures high-speed data transfer and seamless handling of multiple devices. What sets it apart is its diverse power options. All 48 Ethernet ports offer a range of power output choices, including Passive PoE, low voltage PoE, and 802.3af/at (Type 1 \"PoE\" / Type 2 \"PoE+\") with auto-sensing. This feature makes the switch the ultimate solution for powering expansive setups with unparalleled ease and flexibility."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Effortless Networking",
      "text": "With a potent 750W power supply, the CRS354-48P-4S+2Q+RM effortlessly handles power-demanding devices. The cable management bracket that comes with the switch guarantees an organized arrangement, minimizing the need for complex maintenance.\n\nExperience unparalleled networking with a non-blocking throughput of 168 Gbps, a switching capacity of 336 Gbps, and a forwarding rate of 235 Mpps. No more bottlenecks, only seamless data flow."
    }
  ],
